featureType.name: SWCorner_benthic_video_annotations_obs_MBESsubset
featureType.title: Benthic annotations from video observations in SW Corner (WA) - extract from GlobalArchive for area covered by multibeam bathymetry
featureType.abstract: This dataset is an extract from GlobalArchive (https://globalarchive.org/) of publicly available benthic habitat annotations from stereo-BRUV drops in the SW Corner area of Western Australia for the region covered by high-resolution multibeam bathymetry data. These validation points were used as inputs to predicted benthic habitat mapping for this region. This layer has been created for use in a layer package in combination with habitat models. GlobalArchive should be used for download access, and to view more data for the region.
